meta {
  name: 03 Prep pipeline (LLM, guarded)
  seq: 3
}

docs {
  The LLM prep pipeline and its observability/cost surfaces. The POST
  spends real (budget-guarded) LLM money; the three GETs are free reads.
  Four cost guards sit in front of every prep: reuse window, in-flight
  dedupe, concurrency cap, and a rolling 24h budget precheck.
}
